      "UVIndex.java": {
        "text": "/*\n * Simulates UV warnings for a given number of days\n */\npublic class UVIndex {\n\n  private int numDays;\n\n  public UVIndex(int numDays) {\n    this.numDays = numDays;\n  }\n\n  /*\n   * Returns a UV warning for each day\n   */\n  public String generateWarnings() {\n    String result = \"\";\n\n    // ✅ TO DO: Write a for loop that adds lines like:\n    // Day 1: Wear sunscreen!\n    // Day 2: Wear sunscreen!\n    // etc.\n\n    return result;\n  }\n}\n",
